对其排名最小的损耗。这并不是唯一一家收紧腰带的银行，竞争对手高盛（Goldman Sachs）最近&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kSeAdoHVA08iVHbIVKtaatOZi0-Y_EnSuYWsqXqdnwA6m5IAwYQa8RfqZESwkqtJg4oh3UeKZt-7RLfe-mpIvr2HaxMHVGZT8spaYS-9GFqC6S1Uy-nxGzRgvLPKLIwvUEhzX8cej2BOSnr7ZI8Ws4WVEQ8Qi8jUQ-D71VY0mqLunzXCRnTkZUYwfRdwkNtuxZnR_5eZtusksuHQhKwpruBcHKuGBbR1S0VQ42K2fbGxUzcEt0mU5ccUxgSmhEk4TyK7IpQX3ja5bdMe9HtHOx-gQag0PS9191xek3_J6-ubZ2AddBnvwPcrQIiw5CzuCM4ufQP6GUsT-A72xdKjz9V54UbC0gVRxzA1VIpNW3obY13RbkmcrXEdY-w/5bHWzbTto7N_8dMajk0kdMNe40J6lc9g/7" target="_blank"&gt;将其年度员工提升&lt;/a&gt;到今年早些时候。至于花旗集团（Citigroup），它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iqt_U6GoVxBSMJs7s-vytdjPnL14xqyWQ8R2zvkunZw4pITW6hIkdUDfIYG56-ATg-uTtww_dysD6n9hJJDbN0d1svSgLaIIyn-cRg0R0iOxm5P4-BdqB_MUm1DGhHG2157Li_lxPCGK8g1tJfj4V37R-x4uqyaxDxO4mxAmIhbG4e82CT1KX8W2Mf620SPgNgZi7V_LZKbLCyvZY-mgw0G2uWd8V5HfrbNewvGBdoAwwil_mC8A5wuZqZUSEN8dTJbpU7HQrmun9Mm7KSWIO8UCLJ0sF02fhVz3PdKOCKDj1cCwe1wz3TNo0g1n0SaqWe8eLJcNQaWvMNW1MQW7GHrnM4KJxXNSVJ-0YHPyYyfv0Wmiq0LYgp89Dhs/GQfxne3A6rMJQJB94sQ1PNgrUed5myuJ/7" target="_blank"&gt;减少了与该公司周转相关的数百名高级管理人员的支出&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;彭博理工大学：&lt;/strong&gt; 6月4日至5日在旧金山加入顶尖技术决策者和影响者。当我们讨论转变行业及其如何影响社会的进步时，技术在商业，文化和医疗保健中的发展作用。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ho4hnuEHXTi-HX8Bo_ITeEOfVyXB1J3m-fAoK_jGQQM_sAJfV5moi6K4X7ntmHBXqH3oGBFKftlrpse7v9cpynqpT6ySFWkW4k3cy6TgSHKlNBkXap03py9Os9IJRBpVMCuXdjKjdO6cug8X-eqL8-pS7dDeRpFjA45AcO3Sgb0Zo6vDye2tiCUW9J4cRqPdp8lOgZXyatgeuuBFddpckku8hBMmoOASmOvG-ic-Z335dqxa6Bsaz8xQ6ZFCGapXV5NJA8yj6wedQMyixlGXDNwN0MgyHT_7fBiVtfR2vubUGDOMDe3-5FGI84WwslTR32Ym_VH6o7tzsijXtkX5MGeD-zSyoE1-OST2SlCddn7GQZGqnVks8uq1tzWJpPpT7CDbGcfI8bL91csd15TYGnRmw_qHw4SdWga6-st0mG20CYcbYT7HZ742ckVm4GmuDhjJmsSwgNQaY-K760bdAQwBlgGKbpLBVej78M5V83RiuNhxOw_zIzLzgEms-FeChcF1S5oBies_eM_J7aZGoiUBC_8XNbr7923QYdEePLwIXn6Sx0Bc1plF1n47lk2pX6KhSUWabMAujDjltHbmU_3VFZKW4C6dEhspPtxMxisuu23bTv0EX6LnhJmnql6ehzk8dNA4SoGx2Vx